{"tid":103952,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[東京] 箱根+御殿場outlet行程一問","createTime":"2017-02-01T17:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T05:57:18.000Z","uid":11513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a58213d72752d1195a742296266d33de7dd41e","tid":103952,"uid":11513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"小弟二月尾會去箱根，會係箱根stay一晚，亦都想去御殿場outlet行下咁......<br />\n因為第一次去，上網睇又好亂，有少少交通既問題想請教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一日大概行程係咁，第二日先會係箱根玩<br />\n新宿-&gt;箱根湯本(寄行李去酒店)-&gt;御殿場站-&gt;搭shuttle bus去outlet-&gt;行outlet-&gt;御殿場站-&gt;箱根湯本<br />\n<br />\n1. 咁既行程係咪好亂? 有無更好既方法?<br />\n2. 我會買箱根周遊卷，請問下箱根湯本係咪有電車去御殿場站? 係唔係半個鐘一班?<br />\n3. 如果無電車，係咪得返巴士搭? 因為我好驚搭錯巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 來回箱根湯本&lt;-&gt;御殿場站既方法係咪一樣? 我驚行完無車返酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ee2a973e8fcb1ee56ec450bd473eb18215318f","tid":103952,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟二月尾會去箱根，會係箱根stay一晚，亦都想去御殿場outlet行下咁......<br />\n因為第一次去，上網睇又好亂，有少少交通既問題想請教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一日大概行程係咁，第二日先會係箱根玩<br />\n新宿-&amp;gt;箱根湯本(寄行李去酒店)-&amp;gt;御殿場站-&amp;gt;搭shuttle bus去outlet-&amp;gt;行outlet-&amp;gt;御殿場站-&amp;gt;箱根湯本<br />\n<br />\n1. 咁既行程係咪好亂? 有無更好既方法?<br />\n2. 我會買箱根周遊卷，請問下箱根湯本係咪有電車去御殿場站? 係唔係半個鐘一班?<br />\n3. 如果無電車，係咪得返巴士搭? 因為我好驚搭錯巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 來回箱根湯本&amp;lt;-&amp;gt;御殿場站既方法係咪一樣? 我驚行完無車返酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n御殿場站係無鐵路通車去<br />\n你應該係坐巴士喎...<br />\n平日3班車由湯本箱根出發, 2班返轉頭<br />\n再唔係就由強羅出發來回<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.premiumoutlets.co.jp/en/gotemba/access/bus/detail20.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.premiumoutlets.co.jp%2Fen%2Fgotemba%2Faccess%2Fbus%2Fdetail20.html&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a9bf6545\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.premiumoutlets.co.jp/en/gotemba/access/bus/detail20.html</a>"},{"pid":"32ab6aae4da305031eafbf61f999e89627c7b7d4","tid":103952,"uid":55590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T01:35:33.000Z","msg":"一日內應該行得哂"},{"pid":"1321d4ffdf5c815f17ca5742f39f0adac9fc7f3f","tid":103952,"uid":11513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T02:38:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟二月尾會去箱根，會係箱根stay一晚，亦都想去御殿場outlet行下咁......<br />\n因為第一次去，上網睇又好亂，有少少交通既問題想請教大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一日大概行程係咁，第二日先會係箱根玩<br />\n新宿-&amp;amp;gt;箱根湯本(寄行李去酒店)-&amp;amp;gt;御殿場站-&amp;amp;gt;搭shuttle bus去outlet-&amp;amp;gt;行outlet-&amp;amp;gt;御殿場站-&amp;amp;gt;箱根湯本<br />\n<br />\n1. 咁既行程係咪好亂? 有無更好既方法?<br />\n2. 我會買箱根周遊卷，請問下箱根湯本係咪有電車去御殿場站? 係唔係半個鐘一班?<br />\n3. 如果無電車，係咪得返巴士搭? 因為我好驚搭錯巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 來回箱根湯本&amp;amp;lt;-&amp;amp;gt;御殿場站既方法係咪一樣? 我驚行完無車返酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n御殿場站係無鐵路通車去<br />\n你應該係坐巴士喎...<br />\n平日3班車由湯本箱根出發, 2班返轉頭<br />\n再唔係就由強羅出發來回<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.premiumoutlets.co.jp/en/gotemba/access/bus/detail20.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.premiumoutlets.co.jp%2Fen%2Fgotemba%2Faccess%2Fbus%2Fdetail20.html&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a9bf6545\" target=