s%2Fdetail20.html&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a9bf6545\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.premiumoutlets.co.jp/en/gotemba/access/bus/detail20.html</a></blockquote><br />\n即係來回都應該經過強羅？<br />\n跟呢張巴士時間表返黎？<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hakone-tozanbus.co.jp/pdf/13223-002001.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hakone-tozanbus.co.jp%2Fpdf%2F13223-002001.pdf&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a8b263d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hakone-tozanbus.co.jp/pdf/13223-002001.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n係.<br />\n你睇一睇湯本開車個兩班啱唔啱你先<br />\n<br />\n唔啱先經強羅<br />\n返到強羅再搵路返箱根湯本"},{"pid":"4953bf7036b25ed7fb56b4d46b5666359199e34c","tid":103952,"uid":11513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n御殿場站係無鐵路通車去<br />\n你應該係坐巴士喎...<br />\n平日3班車由湯本箱根出發, 2班返轉頭<br />\n再唔係就由強羅出發來回<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.premiumoutlets.co.jp/en/gotemba/access/bus/detail20.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.premiumoutlets.co.jp%2Fen%2Fgotemba%2Faccess%2Fbus%2Fdetail20.html&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a9bf6545\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.premiumoutlets.co.jp/en/gotemba/access/bus/detail20.html</a></blockquote><br />\n即係來回都應該經過強羅？<br />\n跟呢張巴士時間表返黎？<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hakone-tozanbus.co.jp/pdf/13223-002001.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hakone-tozanbus.co.jp%2Fpdf%2F13223-002001.pdf&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a8b263d5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hakone-tozanbus.co.jp/pdf/13223-002001.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n係.<br />\n你睇一睇湯本開車個兩班啱唔啱你先<br />\n<br />\n唔啱先經強羅<br />\n返到強羅再搵路返箱根湯本</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔係好明佢張時間表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n假設我9點出發去御殿場<br />\n3點由御殿場走<br />\n即係應該搭1500班車？"},{"pid":"b9d95e3463a1a442326d817efd8388